::Havotron/Darkwing/Dreadwind::

Havotron turned back to the council.  "Good, some more useful bots will 
be appreciated."
'Hmm Apeface and Slugslinger are scared, good, they will follow my lead. 
But I like this Spinister even more.  He was not scared of my awsome 
power, though he should be.  He may be the one to wield me.' Havotron 
thought silently to himself.

Darkwing stood weakly. "I am sorry my master." he said holding back his 
pain.

Dreadwind also backed off to support his brother.

Havotron spoke once again.  "They must learn my council members.  They 
will not anger me again. Now if that is all i have affairs i must attend 
too."
